    <url>/2024/11/11/doris/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="Doris坏盘换盘方法"><a href="#Doris坏盘换盘方法" class="headerlink" title="Doris坏盘换盘方法"></a>Doris坏盘换盘方法</h1><h2 id="先换好盘"><a href="#先换好盘" class="headerlink" title="先换好盘"></a>先换好盘</h2><p>参考其它&#x2F;data，创建好目录，正确授权。</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> /</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">mkdir</span> -p /doris-storage</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">chown</span> -R doris:doris /doris-storage</span><br><span class="line">ll</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="注释掉坏盘路径"><a href="#注释掉坏盘路径" class="headerlink" title="注释掉坏盘路径"></a>注释掉坏盘路径</h2><figure class="highlight vim"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">vi</span> /usr/local/doris-<span class="keyword">be</span>/<span class="keyword">conf</span>/be_custom.<span class="keyword">conf</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><img src="/vx_images/46833146873345.png"><br>注释掉broken_storage_path。</p>
<h2 id="重启be进程"><a href="#重启be进程" class="headerlink" title="重启be进程"></a>重启be进程</h2><p>可在Web管理控制台操作。</p>
]]></content>
